Shane Lee Lindstrom -LRB- born February 11 , 1994 -RRB- , professionally known as Murda Beatz , is a Canadian hip hop record producer from Fort Erie , Ontario .
He is noted for producing songs such as `` No Shopping '' by rapper French Montana , `` Back on Road '' by rapper Gucci Mane , Lindstrom has also produced several tracks for various artists such as Drake , Migos , Travis Scott and PartyNextDoor , among others .